primary.context: Caller had questions regarding a maintenance bill and ownership info
primary.detail: The agent verified the caller and provided the address and owner name on file.

steps: Agent identified the request as a maintenance bill inquiry.
Agent performed account lookup via phone number.
Agent verified identity after a name mismatch (Vincent vs Valerie).
Agent provided the address on file upon request.
Agent confirmed the owner name and contract details.
Caller confirmed no further assistance was needed.

clarifications.note: Agent asked for spelling due to name mismatch

actions.detail: Verified Valerie Creo in New Jersey

insights.summary: The caller wanted to verify billing details and ownership information. The AI successfully looked up the account, handled a name mismatch gracefully, and provided the requested data.
